Below is an enterprise-grade Jira audit toolkit used before migrations from **Jira Data Center / Jira Server to Jira Cloud.
It is designed for large environments (1k–10k projects, 50k+ workflows, heavy scripting) and focuses on:
automation discovery
script extraction
migration risk detection
configuration complexity scoring
The toolkit structure mirrors what is typically used in enterprise migration readiness assessments.
