26. Workflow Complexity Scoring
Example heuristic:
SQL
Copy code
SELECT
workflowname,
LENGTH(descriptor) AS size,
CASE
 WHEN LENGTH(descriptor)>20000 THEN 'HIGH'
 WHEN LENGTH(descriptor)>10000 THEN 'MEDIUM'
 ELSE 'LOW'
END complexity
FROM jiraworkflows
ORDER BY size DESC;
27. Project Automation Risk Score
Example calculation:
SQL
Copy code
SELECT
p.pkey,
count(w.workflowname) AS workflows
FROM project p
JOIN nodeassociation na
 ON na.source_node_id=p.id
JOIN workflowscheme ws
 ON ws.id=na.sink_node_id
JOIN workflowschemeentity wse
 ON wse.scheme=ws.id
JOIN jiraworkflows w
 ON w.workflowname=wse.workflow
GROUP BY p.pkey
ORDER BY workflows DESC;
